'''美洲大獎賽'''（{{lang-en|Grand Prix of America}}）<ref name="GPofA">{{cite news | url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/formula1/15440153 | title=New Jersey to host Grand Prix of America in 2013 | date=2011-10-25 | accessdate=2014-07-01 | archive-date=2014-02-01 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140201115909/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/formula1/15440153 | dead-url=no }}</ref>是一場於2011年提議舉辦的[[一級方程式|一級方程式]]（F1）世界錦標賽賽事。<ref name="NJ delay">{{cite news|title=New Jersey Grand Prix to be postponed until 2014|url=http://www.autosport.com/news/report.php/id/103529|work=Autosport.com|publisher=[[Haymarket_Media_Group|Haymarket Publications]]|date=2012-10-19|accessdate=2012-10-19|archive-date=2017-02-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170225030415/http://www.autosport.com/news/report.php/id/103529|dead-url=no}}</ref>這場賽事計劃舉辦於[[帝國碼頭市街賽道|帝國碼頭市街賽道]]，賽道總長5.2公里，途經[[紐澤西州|紐澤西州]][[威霍肯_(新泽西州)|威霍肯]]與{{link-en|西紐約|West New York, New Jersey}}城鎮，<ref name="GPofA"/>緊鄰著{{le|威霍肯帝國港|Weehawken Port Imperial}}，<ref name="Autosport 10-25">{{cite news | url = http://www.autosport.com/news/report.php/id/95669 | title = New Jersey confirms F1 grand prix from the 2013 season | publisher = [[Haymarket_Press|Haymarket Press]] | work = [[Autosport|Autosport.com]] | last = Elizalde | first = Pablo | date = 2011-10-25 | accessdate = 2011-10-25 | archiveurl = https://www.webcitation.org/62hv9VxtQ?url=http://www.autosport.com/news/report.php/id/95669 | archivedate = 2011年10月25日 | deadurl = yes }}</ref>更能夠盡覽[[紐約市摩天大樓列表|紐約市摩天大樓]]天際線。

美洲大獎賽原定於2013年6月登場，<ref>Baime, A.J. [https://www.wsj.com/articles/SB10001424052970204777904576653552767815670 "Formula One Roars to Banks of Hudson"] {{Wayback|url=https://www.wsj.com/articles/SB10001424052970204777904576653552767815670 |date=20180618175323 }}, ''[[The_Wall_Street_Journal|The Wall Street Journal]]'', October 26, 2011. Accessed October 27, 2011. "Formula One...  will hold a Grand Prix race on the banks of the Hudson River against the backdrop of the Manhattan skyline in June 2013."</ref> 卻在2013年告吹。<ref>[http://www.northjersey.com/news/weehawken-s-formula-one-grand-prix-race-delayed-again-1.1057055 "Weehawken's Formula One Grand Prix race delayed again"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.northjersey.com/news/weehawken-s-formula-one-grand-prix-race-delayed-again-1.1057055 |date=20160808125713 }}, ''[[The_Record_(Bergen_County)|The Record (Bergen County)]]'', July 24, 2014. Accessed August 4, 2016.</ref><ref name="FIA Calendar2">{{cite web|url=http://www.fia.com/news/world-motor-sport-council-2|title=World Motor Sport Council|accessdate=2017-08-29|date=2013-09-27|website=fia.com|archive-date=2013-09-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130927151146/http://www.fia.com/news/world-motor-sport-council-2|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite press release|title=The final 2013 meeting of the FIA World Motor Sport Council (WMSC) took place today (4 December) in Paris, France.|publisher=FIA|date=2013-12-04|url=http://www.fia.com/news/world-motor-sport-council-3|accessdate=2013-12-04|archive-date=2013-12-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131207060641/http://www.fia.com/news/world-motor-sport-council-3|dead-url=no}}</ref>2013年底，一級方程式賽車總裁兼首席執行官[[伯尼·埃克萊斯頓|伯尼·埃克萊斯頓]]表示，由於發起人違約而未能順利舉辦，不過，仍歡迎其他組織呈報新的提案。<ref name="breach2">{{cite news|url=http://www.autoweek.com/article/20131224/F1/131229938|title=New Jersey Grand Prix organizers in breach of contract says Ecclestone Formula One boss says if another group wants to take over Grand Prix of America, 'they can have it'|last=Sylt|first=Christian|date=2013-12-24|publisher=Auto Week|accessdate=2013-12-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140608153525/http://www.autoweek.com/article/20131224/f1/131229938|archive-date=2014-06-08|dead-url=yes}}</ref>這場比賽反反覆覆的出現在一級方程式賽車暫定賽程表中，直到2016年便不曾再出現在暫定賽程表上了。<ref>{{cite press release|title=World Motor Sport Council 2014 - Beijing|publisher=FIA|date=2014-09-04|url=http://www.fia.com/news/world-motor-sport-council-2014-beijing|accessdate=2014-09-12|archive-date=2019-04-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190412190336/https://www.fia.com/news/world-motor-sport-council-2014-beijing|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 歷史 ==
1983年賽季，賽會官方曾宣布將會在{{le|梅多蘭茲體育中心|Meadowlands Sports Complex}}、[[法拉盛草原可樂娜公園|法拉盛草原可樂娜公園]]的草原湖，或是[[長島_(紐約)|長島]][[亨普斯特德|亨普斯特德]]的{{le|米爾切空軍基地|Mitchel Field}}（與1936及1937年的{{le|范德比爾特杯|Vanderbilt Cups}}舉辦地相同）中擇一地，舉辦一場位於[[紐約都會區|紐約都會區]]的大獎賽。<ref>{{cite news|title=New York May Get '83 Auto Grand Prix|url=http://www.nytimes.com/1982/10/28/sports/new-york-may-get-83-auto-grand-prix.html|accessdate=2011-05-18|newspaper=[[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]]|date=1982-10-28|archive-date=2013-06-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130618040641/http://www.nytimes.com/1982/10/28/sports/new-york-may-get-83-auto-grand-prix.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=New York Grand Prix scheduled|url=http://news.google.com/newspapers?id=tdExAAAAIBAJ&sjid=zeMFAAAAIBAJ&pg=4398,5763243|accessdate=2011-05-18|newspaper=[[Reading_Eagle|Reading Eagle]]|date=1982-10-28|agency=[[UPI|UPI]]|pages=41, 47|archive-date=2015-11-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151122145105/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=tdExAAAAIBAJ&sjid=zeMFAAAAIBAJ&pg=4398,5763243|dead-url=no}}</ref>然而，這場比賽首次被推延後又宣告取消。之後，又經過{{Le|1984年世界一級方程式錦標賽|1984 FIA Formula One World Championship|1984}}及{{Le|1985年世界一級方程式錦標賽|1985 FIA Formula One World Championship|1985年}}的計劃後卻始終未果。<ref>{{cite news|url=https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=3j9UAAAAIBAJ&sjid=uo0DAAAAIBAJ&pg=5607,698774|title=No auto racing in New York|date=1983-06-03|newspaper=[[Boca_Raton_News|Boca Raton News]]|accessdate=2011-05-18|page=2D|archive-date=2015-11-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151122160043/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=3j9UAAAAIBAJ&sjid=uo0DAAAAIBAJ&pg=5607,698774|dead-url=no}}</ref>{{le|梅多蘭茲大獎賽|Meadowlands Grand Prix|梅多蘭茲}}則成了 {{le|冠軍方程式|Champ Car}}的比賽場地。<ref>{{cite news|url=https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=-DAqAAAAIBAJ&sjid=TkcEAAAAIBAJ&pg=3145,5557235|title=U.S. Grand Prix success is vital to CART future|last=Harris|first=Mike|date=1984-06-29|newspaper=[[The_Daily_News_(Kentucky)|Daily News]]|accessdate=2011-05-18|location=Bowling Green, Kentucky{{!}}Bowling Green, KY|agency=[[Associated_Press|AP]]|page=1-B|archive-date=2015-11-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151122134242/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=-DAqAAAAIBAJ&sjid=TkcEAAAAIBAJ&pg=3145,5557235|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2010年5月，一級方程式老闆[[伯尼·埃克萊斯頓|伯尼·埃克萊斯頓]]宣布，他計畫在[[2012年世界一級方程式錦標賽|2012年賽季]]將一級方程式比賽在帶到[[紐約市|紐約市]]。埃克萊斯頓表示這場賽事將會在[[紐澤西州|紐澤西州]]的[[哈德遜河|哈德遜河]]畔舉辦，並且能從[[曼哈頓|曼哈頓]]天際線綜覽整條賽道。<ref>{{cite web |last=Lostia |first=Michele |title=Ecclestone hoping for New York GP |url=http://www.autosport.com/news/report.php/id/82366 |work=[[Autosport|Autosport]].com |date=2010-03-25 |accessdate=2014-07-01 |archive-date=2014-11-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141109183926/http://www.autosport.com/news/report.php/id/82366 |dead-url=no }}</ref>一個月後，有關在[[澤西市|澤西市]]的{{le|自由州立公園|Liberty State Park}}興建賽道的計畫逐一浮出檯面，<ref>{{cite web |title=New York F1 track plans revealed – Jersey City bids for 2012 night race |url=http://www.f1fanatic.co.uk/2010/05/04/new-york-f1-track-plans-revealed-jersey-city-bids-for-new-night-race-in-2012/ |first=Keith |last=Collantine |work=F1 Fanatic |date=2010-05-04 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5w707hQJk?url=http://www.f1fanatic.co.uk/2010/05/04/new-york-f1-track-plans-revealed-jersey-city-bids-for-new-night-race-in-2012/ |archivedate=2011年1月30日 |accessdate=2010-05-04 |deadurl=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |last=Noble |first=Jonathan |title=Jersey City eyes Formula 1 race |url=http://www.autosport.com/news/report.php/id/83312 |work=[[Autosport|Autosport]].com |date=2010-05-04 |accessdate=2014-07-01 |archive-date=2014-11-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141109185520/http://www.autosport.com/news/report.php/id/83312 |dead-url=no }}</ref>不過，這些計畫不久後也胎死腹中。<ref>{{cite web |last=Elizalde |first=Pablo |title=Jersey City cans F1 grand prix plan |url=http://www.autosport.com/news/report.php/id/83332 |work=[[Autosport|Autosport]].com |date=2010-05-05 |accessdate=2014-07-01 |archive-date=2014-11-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141109184016/http://www.autosport.com/news/report.php/id/83332 |dead-url=no }}</ref>其後，更針對[[史泰登島|史泰登島]]、{{le|弗洛伊德·貝內特機場|Floyd Bennett Field}}和梅多蘭茲進行探勘，但是沒有一處是可行的。<ref name="WSJ">{{cite news|title=Formula One Roars To Banks of Hudson|url=http://online.wsj.com/article/SB10001424052970204777904576653552767815670.html|first=A.J.|last=Baime|work=The Wall Street Journal|publisher=[[News_Corporation|News Corporation]]|date=2011-10-25|accessdate=2011-10-26|archive-date=2011-10-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111028172039/http://online.wsj.com/article/SB10001424052970204777904576653552767815670.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2011年8月，《[[華爾街日報|華爾街日報]]》報導一則關於在紐澤西州[[威霍肯_(新泽西州)|威霍肯]]與{{link-en|西紐約|West New York, New Jersey}}規劃市街賽道的計劃，並指出其可望在2013年登場。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.f1fanatic.co.uk/2011/08/03/new-jersey-f1-track-new-york/|title=New plans for New York Grand Prix track in 2013|last=Collantine|first=Keith|date=2011-08-03|publisher=F1Fanatic|accessdate=2011-10-26|archive-date=2011-10-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111026205647/http://www.f1fanatic.co.uk/2011/08/03/new-jersey-f1-track-new-york/|dead-url=no}}</ref>兩個月後，《華爾街日報》更進一步報導，這場賽事預定將會在2013年6月舉行。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://online.wsj.com/article/SB10001424052970204618704576645651553992120.html?mod=googlenews_wsj|title=Formula One Is Coming to New Jersey in 2013|last=Baime|first=A.J.|date=2011-10-22|work=The Wall Street Journal|accessdate=2011-10-26|location=New York}}</ref>然而，其他報社則保持著相對謹慎的態度，他們認為仍需待[[哈德遜郡|哈德遜郡]]官方批准後，才得以評估這場比賽的可行性。修訂版提案在隔月出爐，<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/sport/2011/oct/25/formula-one-new-jersey-gp|title=Formula One to unveil New Jersey Grand Prix for 2013|last=Reuters|date=2011-10-25|work=The Guardian|location=London|accessdate=2011-10-26|archive-date=2011-10-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111026002414/http://www.guardian.co.uk/sport/2011/oct/25/formula-one-new-jersey-gp|dead-url=no}}</ref>市街賽道將沿著{{le|威霍肯帝國港|Weehawken Port Imperial|帝國港}}行駛後爬升至{{le|哈德遜峭壁|The Palisades (Hudson River)}}，接上{{le|東方大道|Boulevard East}}，之後回到帝國港大道。2011年10月25日，官方證實紐澤西州將從2013年起，在一條長3.2英里（5.2公里）的市街賽道舉辦美洲大獎賽。<ref name="Autosport 10-25" /><ref>{{Citation | last = Schultz | first = Johnathon | title = Plan for a New York Area Formula One Race Announced in New Jersey | newspaper = The New York Times | date = 2011-10-26 | url = http://wheels.blogs.nytimes.com/2011/10/25/bid-for-a-new-york-area-formula-one-race-announced-in-new-jersey/?scp=1&sq=grand%20prix%20of%20america&st=cse | accessdate = 2011-10-27 | archive-date = 2014-01-06 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20140106032808/http://wheels.blogs.nytimes.com/2011/10/25/bid-for-a-new-york-area-formula-one-race-announced-in-new-jersey/?scp=1&sq=grand%20prix%20of%20america&st=cse | dead-url = no }}</ref>

自2013年6月起，這場賽事的舉辦合約共計10年，此外，也不會影響到11月舉辦於[[美洲赛道|奧斯丁]]的[[美國大獎賽|美國大獎賽]]。<ref name="Joe">{{cite news|title=Details from New Jersey|url=http://joesaward.wordpress.com/2011/10/25/details-from-new-jersey/|first=Joe|last=Saward|work=Joe Saward on F1|publisher=Joe Saward|date=2011-10-25|accessdate=2011-10-26|archive-date=2011-10-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111028000247/http://joesaward.wordpress.com/2011/10/25/details-from-new-jersey/|dead-url=yes}}</ref>這場比賽將與{{le|吉爾維倫紐夫賽道|Circuit Gilles Villeneuve|蒙特婁}}的[[加拿大大獎賽|加拿大大獎賽]]成為「搭檔賽事」，兩場比賽僅會相隔一週，以減少物流方面的開銷。<ref name="Joe"/>

[[全國運動汽車競賽協會|全國運動汽車競賽協會]]的長期主辦人{{le|漢姆皮·惠勒|Humpy Wheeler}}擔任賽事顧問，他預估這場賽事將會為紐約州與紐澤西州地區每年帶來超過一億美元的經濟效益。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://mobile.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-25/formula-one-s-grand-prix-of-america-to-be-run-in-new-jersey-near-manhattan?category=%2F|title=Formula One Cars to Race in New Jersey in 2013, F1 CEO Ecclestone Says|last=Dopp|first=Terrence|date=2011-10-25|publisher=Bloomberg|accessdate=2011-10-26|location=New York|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120401062406/http://mobile.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-25/formula-one-s-grand-prix-of-america-to-be-run-in-new-jersey-near-manhattan?category=%2F|archive-date=2012-04-01|dead-url=yes}}</ref>賽事承辦人兼董事由{{Le|利奧·欣德利|Leo Hindery|小利奧·欣德利}}出任，而丹尼斯·羅賓遜（Dennis Robinson）則擔任-{zh-tw:營運長;zh-cn:首席运营官}-。湯姆·科特（Tom Cotter）在2012年8月20日辭去了總裁一職。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/sport/formulaone/article-2191520/USA-Grand-Prix-president-Tom-Cotter-quits.html|title=More woe for US GP as president Cotter quits just seven months into role|last=Sportsmail Reporter|publisher=Daily Mail|date=2012-08-21|accessdate=2012-08-31|archive-date=2012-08-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120830111256/http://www.dailymail.co.uk/sport/formulaone/article-2191520/USA-Grand-Prix-president-Tom-Cotter-quits.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

[[赫爾曼·提爾克|赫爾曼·提爾克]]公司的克里斯蒂安·埃普（Christian Epp）曾表示，這條賽道的佈局涵蓋類似於摩納哥市街賽道的海拔高度變化，但是，特別之處在於這裡有著比其他市街賽道更快的車速。<ref name="US Grand Prix Packages">{{cite news|title=US Grand Prix of America|url=http://www.usgppackages.com/us-grand-prix/grand-prix-america/|date=2013-10-18|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131019125112/http://www.usgppackages.com/us-grand-prix/grand-prix-america/|archivedate=2013年10月19日}}</ref>

=== 延期 ===
2012年7月，[[伯尼·埃克萊斯頓|伯尼·埃克萊斯頓]]證實紐澤西州將會以'''（紐約）澤西大獎賽'''（{{lang-en|Grand Prix of Jersey (New York)}}）之名，登錄在[[國際汽車聯盟|國際汽車聯盟]]的2013年大獎賽賽程表當中，<ref>{{cite web | title = FIA releases 2013 calendar | publisher = Formula 1 | date = September 2012 | url = http://www.formula1.com/news/headlines/2012/9/13853.html | accessdate = 2013-01-22 | archive-date = 2013-01-28 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20130128021845/http://www.formula1.com/news/headlines/2012/9/13853.html | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name="GPofNJ">{{cite news|title=FIA confirms 2013 F1 calendar with minor changes|url=http://www.f1fanatic.co.uk/2012/09/28/fia-confirms-2013-f1-calendar-minor/|first=Keith|last=Collatine|work=F1 Fanatic|publisher=Keith Collantine|date=2012-09-28|accessdate=2012-10-01|archive-date=2012-10-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121001034011/http://www.f1fanatic.co.uk/2012/09/28/fia-confirms-2013-f1-calendar-minor/|dead-url=no}}</ref>同年9月，官方暫定將這場比賽安排於2013年6月16日舉辦。<ref name="21 Sept. calendar">{{cite news|title=Singapore GP: 2013 Formula 1 calendar revealed|url=http://www.autosport.com/news/report.php/id/102674|first1=Jonathan|last1=Noble|first2=Dieter|last2=Rencken|work=|publisher=[[Haymarket_Media_Group|Haymarket Publications]]|date=2012-09-21|accessdate=2012-09-21|archive-date=2017-02-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170216021913/http://www.autosport.com/news/report.php/id/102674|dead-url=no}}</ref>然而，埃克萊斯頓卻在幾天後宣布廢除比賽合約。<ref name=doubts>{{cite web | url=http://www.autosport.com/news/report.php/id/102851 | title=Fresh doubts emerge over 2013 New Jersey Grand Prix | publisher=[[Haymarket_Media_Group|Haymarket Publications]] | work=Autosport.com | date=2012-09-25 | accessdate=2012-09-25 | author=Beer, Matt | archive-date=2012-09-25 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120925132129/http://www.autosport.com/news/report.php/id/102851 | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{citation|title=Formula One race in New Jersey may not happen|newspaper=The Star-Ledger|date=2012-09-25|url=http://www.nj.com/news/index.ssf/2012/09/formula_1_race_in_nj_may_not_l.html#incart_river_default|accessdate=2012-09-27|archive-date=2012-09-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120928100355/http://www.nj.com/news/index.ssf/2012/09/formula_1_race_in_nj_may_not_l.html#incart_river_default|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{citation|last=Sylt|first=Christine|title=Grand Prix of America in serious doubt after organizers' contract is torn up|newspaper=The Guardian|date=2012-09-25|url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/sport/2012/sep/25/grand-prix-america-contract-torn-up?INTCMP=SRCH|accessdate=2012-09-27}}</ref>

2012年9月，埃克萊斯頓宣布由於承辦人無法遵從合約的條件，致使比賽合約被終止。<ref name=doubts/>然而，這場比賽仍舊暫時以「待確定」的狀態包含在[[2013年世界一級方程式錦標賽|2013年一級方程式賽曆]]中。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://formula-one.speedtv.com/article/f1-new-jersey-on-2013-calendar-but-to-be-confirmed|title=F1: New Jersey On 2013 Calendar But 'To Be Confirmed'|last=Cooper|first=Adam|date=2012-09-28|work=SPEED Channel|publisher=Fox Sports|accessdate=2012-09-28|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121001011936/http://formula-one.speedtv.com/article/f1-new-jersey-on-2013-calendar-but-to-be-confirmed/|archivedate=2012年10月1日}}</ref>正式賽程表也在2012年12月敲定。<ref>{{citation|last=Baime|first=A.J.|author2=Heather Haddon|title=Uncertainty Over N.J. Formula One|newspaper=The Wall Street Journal|date=2012-10-01|url=http://online.wsj.com/article/SB10000872396390444004704578030842152769304.html|accessdate=2012-10-03|archive-date=2012-10-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121004233651/http://online.wsj.com/article/SB10000872396390444004704578030842152769304.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>2012年10月18日，威霍肯市長宣布這場賽事延期至2014年舉行。<ref name="NJ delay"/><ref>.{{citation | last = McDonald | first = Terrace | title = Mayors: Formula 1 race along Hudson River waterfront postponed until 2014 | newspaper = The Jersey Journal | date = 2012-10-18 | url = http://www.nj.com/hudson/index.ssf/2012/10/mayors_formula_1_race_along_hu.html | accessdate = 2012-10-18 | quote =  | archive-date = 2012-10-19 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20121019234910/http://www.nj.com/hudson/index.ssf/2012/10/mayors_formula_1_race_along_hu.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>當被問到延期的原因時，埃克萊斯頓回應表示，承辦單位無法如期籌備在2013年舉辦比賽的一切所需。<ref>{{cite news|title=New Jersey race to be postponed - organisers|url=http://uk.reuters.com/article/2012/10/19/motor-racing-americas-idUKL3E8LJ3NY20121019|first=Alan|last=Baldwin|work=[[Reuters|Reuters UK]]|publisher=[[Thompson_Reuters|Thompson Reuters]]|date=2012-10-19|accessdate=2012-10-20|archive-date=2014-03-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140330065935/http://uk.reuters.com/article/2012/10/19/motor-racing-americas-idUKL3E8LJ3NY20121019|dead-url=no}}</ref>

賽事發起人小利奧·欣德利在2013年3月表示美洲大獎賽將回重返到這條賽道，並已安排在9月左右展開道路鋪銑工程。<ref>{{cite news|title=New Jersey F1 Race Promoter Hindery Jr. Says 'We Are Back Under Construction'|url=http://www.sportsbusinessdaily.com/Global/Issues/2013/03/08/Events-and-Attractions/New-Jersey-F1.aspx|first=HJ|last=Mai|work=SportsBusiness Journal|date=2013-03-08|accessdate=2013-03-08|archive-date=2013-03-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130310050840/http://www.sportsbusinessdaily.com/Global/Issues/2013/03/08/Events-and-Attractions/New-Jersey-F1.aspx|dead-url=no}}</ref>

然而，欣德利的組織長期陷入財務困境，且他們始終不清楚如何籌措資金。紐澤西州州長[[克里斯·克里斯帝|克里斯·克里斯帝]]更表示，這是一場與其他運動賽事相當的比賽，州政府無從挪用補助金。媒體於2013年5月的報導推測指出，儘管伯尼·埃克萊斯頓表示與欣德利的僵局會談仍有機會重啟，<ref>{{cite web|url=http://en.espnf1.com/f1/motorsport/story/106898.html|title=Ecclestone confirms Long Beach talks Caroline Reid and Christian Sylt|accessdate=2013-05-08|date=2013-04-30|last=Reid|first=Caroline|publisher=ESPN|last2=Sylt|first2=Christian|archive-date=2013-05-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130504215516/http://en.espnf1.com/f1/motorsport/story/106898.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>但是，他卻已著手計劃讓一級方程式賽車回歸{{le|長灘大獎賽|Grand Prix of Long Beach|長灘賽道}}，以作為紐澤西的替代方案，<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.nj.com/news/index.ssf/2013/05/for_nj_formula_1_race_more_bum.html#incart_river|title=N.J. Formula 1 race, more bumps in the road|last=Strunsky|first=Steve|date=2013-05-08|newspaper=The Star-Ledger|accessdate=2013-05-08|archive-date=2013-06-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130606183514/http://www.nj.com/news/index.ssf/2013/05/for_nj_formula_1_race_more_bum.html#incart_river|dead-url=no}}</ref>更指出該項運動的行政人員已經在這場賽事投入資金，以還清承辦單位的債款，並且加快施工進度。原先在[[長灘_(加利福尼亞州)|長灘]]創辦{{le|美西大獎賽|United States Grand Prix West}}的克里斯·普克（Chris Pook）也成為了美洲大獎賽的顧問。<ref>{{cite news|title=F1 has invested in New Jersey race, says Ecclestone|url=http://uk.reuters.com/article/2013/05/11/motor-racing-usa-jersey-idUKL3N0DS09120130511|first=Alan|last=Baldwin|work=reuters.com|publisher=[[Reuters|Reuters]]|date=2013-05-11|accessdate=2013-05-12|archive-date=2013-06-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130625080454/http://uk.reuters.com/article/2013/05/11/motor-racing-usa-jersey-idUKL3N0DS09120130511|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2013年6月，賽事承辦者小利奧·欣德利宣布取得所有的執照，並與一級方程式總裁伯尼·埃克萊斯頓簽下了一紙全新的15年合約。<ref>{{cite news|title=Local Formula 1 organizer says he has new contract, NJ race on schedule for June 2014|url=http://www.nj.com/news/index.ssf/2013/06/local_formula_1_organizer_says.html|first=Steve|last=Strunsky|work=www.nj.com/starledger|publisher=[[The_Star-Ledger|The Star-Ledger]]|date=2013-06-07|accessdate=2013-06-07|archive-date=2013-06-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130610033331/http://www.nj.com/news/index.ssf/2013/06/local_formula_1_organizer_says.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>永久的24輛車的車庫工程也幾近完成，而路面鋪銑工程最快將在次週進行，<ref>{{cite news|title=N.J. Formula One Race Is 'Definitely On'|url=http://online.wsj.com/article/SB10001424127887324299104578531323487479656.html|first=AJ|last=Baime|work=wsj.com|publisher=[[Wall_Street_Journal|Wall Street Journal]]|date=2013-06-07|accessdate=2013-06-07|archive-date=2013-06-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130608130712/http://online.wsj.com/article/SB10001424127887324299104578531323487479656.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>遠遠超過原定於2013年9月的動工時間。

2013年8月23日，埃克萊斯頓宣布由於賽事發起人無法籌備賽事策畫所需的一億美元，將終止舉辦2014年美洲大獎賽。<ref>{{cite web   | last =    | first =    | title = F1: 2014 Grand Prix of America is off, says Bernie   | publisher = CNN   | date = 2013-08-23   | url = http://edition.cnn.com/2013/08/23/sport/motorsport/f1-grand-prix-america-ecclestone/   | accessdate =    | archive-date = 2014-07-28   | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20140728231838/http://edition.cnn.com/2013/08/23/sport/motorsport/f1-grand-prix-america-ecclestone/   | dead-url = no   }}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.roadandtrack.com/racing/racing-news/ecclestone-says-no-2014-grand-prix-of-america?src=rss|title=F1's Ecclestone says no 2014 Grand Prix of America in NJ|date=2013-08-23|accessdate=2014-07-06|work=roadandtrack.com|publisher=earst Communications|first=Zach|last=Bowman|archive-date=2013-11-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131103155824/http://www.roadandtrack.com/racing/racing-news/ecclestone-says-no-2014-grand-prix-of-america?src=rss|dead-url=no}}</ref>最終，這場賽事並未包含在[[2014年世界一級方程式錦標賽#2014年賽歷|2014年賽曆]]當中，<ref>{{cite web   | last = Benson   | first = Andrew   | title = Formula 1: New Jersey race dropped from draft 2014 calendar   | publisher = BBC Sport   | date = 2013-09-05   | url = http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/formula1/23974794   | accessdate = 2013-09-05   | archive-date = 2013-09-05   | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20130905221953/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/formula1/23974794   | dead-url = no   }}</ref>而賽事發起人則聲稱這是行政疏失。<ref>{{cite web   | last = Smith   | first = Luke   | title = New Jersey GP still could claim place on 2014 F1 calendar   | publisher = NBC Sports   | date = 2013-09-06   | url = http://motorsportstalk.nbcsports.com/2013/09/06/new-jersey-gp-still-could-claim-place-on-2014-f1-calendar/   | accessdate = 2013-09-11   | archive-date = 2013-09-08   | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20130908135144/http://motorsportstalk.nbcsports.com/2013/09/06/new-jersey-gp-still-could-claim-place-on-2014-f1-calendar/   | dead-url = no   }}</ref>

在2013年9月22日的[[2013年新加坡大獎賽|2013年新加坡大獎賽]]電視轉播期間，小利奧·欣德利與其他發起人表示他們已經遞交全額費用，並將比賽暫定於2014年6月1日（在摩納哥與加拿大大獎賽之間）舉行。<ref>{{cite news|title=Door left open for New Jersey F1 race on 2014 grand prix calendar|url=http://www.autosport.com/news/report.php/id/110055|first=Jonathan|last=Noble|work=www.autosport.com|publisher=[[Autosport|Autosport]]|date=2013-09-21|accessdate=2013-09-23|archive-date=2013-09-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130924054848/http://www.autosport.com/news/report.php/id/110055|dead-url=no}}</ref>隨後，這場大獎賽確實登錄於暫定的賽程表中。<ref name="FIA Calendar">{{cite news|url=http://www.fia.com/news/world-motor-sport-council-2|title=World Motor Sport Council|date=2013-09-27|work=fia.com|publisher=[[FIA|FIA]]|accessdate=2014-07-06|archive-date=2013-09-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130927151146/http://www.fia.com/news/world-motor-sport-council-2|dead-url=no}}</ref>2013年12月4日，國際汽車聯盟發布正式的2014年世界一級方程式錦標賽賽曆，卻沒有包含這場大獎賽。同時，國際汽車聯盟宣布因為一些長期的財政問題無法如期解決，所以延緩了這場大獎賽。埃克萊斯頓自己似乎還沒放棄這場賽事；他肯定能在2015年舉辦這場大獎賽。承辦單位則持續進行財政重建，持續保持著樂觀的態度。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://grandprix247.com/2013/12/04/new-jersey-mexico-india-south-korea-dropped-from-19-raced-2013-f1-calendar/|title=2014 F1 CALENDAR DOWN TO 19 RACES AS NEW JERSEY, MEXICO, INDIA, KOREA DROPPED|date=2013-12-04|work=grandprix247.com|publisher=Grand Prix 247|accessdate=2014-07-06|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://archive.is/20131204180836/http://grandprix247.com/2013/12/04/new-jersey-mexico-india-south-korea-dropped-from-19-raced-2013-f1-calendar/|archivedate=2013-12-04}}</ref>2013年12月，埃克萊斯頓表示承辦單位違約，而他也樂意接受其他組織提出的建議。<ref name="breach">{{cite news|url=http://www.autoweek.com/article/20131224/F1/131229938?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=feed&utm_campaign=|title=New Jersey Grand Prix organizers in breach of contract says Ecclestone Formula One boss says if another group wants to take over Grand Prix of America, 'they can have it'|last=Sylt|first=Christian|date=2013-12-24|publisher=Auto Week|accessdate=2013-12-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140101102419/http://www.autoweek.com/article/20131224/F1/131229938?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=feed&utm_campaign=|archive-date=2014-01-01|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

2014年，關乎這場比賽的新聞寥寥無幾，直到《[[富比士|富比士]]》於7月洩露欣德利已找到投資者資助舉辦比賽，不過他們卻在最後一刻宣告退出。另一方面，埃克萊斯頓則透露他不願在2016年前將比賽納入一級方程式賽程表中。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.forbes.com/sites/csylt/2014/07/24/f1-will-race-in-azerbaijan-in-2016-says-ecclestone/|title=F1 Will Race In Azerbaijan In 2016 Says Ecclestone|accessdate=2017-08-29|website=www.forbes.com|archive-date=2017-07-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170729120058/https://www.forbes.com/sites/csylt/2014/07/24/f1-will-race-in-azerbaijan-in-2016-says-ecclestone/|dead-url=no}}</ref>目前並沒有更進一步的消息，自{{F1|2015}}賽季展開後，這場比賽的關注度便逐漸下滑。

